                    <span>A fabulous collection of soul-stirring preaching by one of this century's finest preachers. Many people know King as a great political leader, fiery orator, and creative organizer. This collection of sermons will convince  the world that King was first and foremost an anointed preacher. His  sermons ring with authenticity and resound with relevancy. Kings messages  speak profoundly to our troubled times and offer both prophetic insight and  divine guidance as we attempt to find our way into the next millinium. This  collection of sermons, with their superb introductions and commentaries, is  perhaps one of the finest efforts of its kind. It will certainly be a  source of pleasure and insight for generations to come.</span>
                  
