                    <span>A Knock At Midnight is frightfully prophetic,subperbly truthful and dynamically inspiring.It shows what the great mind of King brings and brought to the forefront while he was living and while he continues to live  in our hearts.These sermons are chillingly lifelike as if King speaks  directly to your heart and mind---NOW! It is truly a must read! The sermon  A Knock at Midnight delivers the powerful and sensitive message concerning  where the Church has to take the people as far as their needs are concerned  and it deals with the advocacy of having to open the door to the truly  oppressed and needy.It is a thought provoking  theme set against the veil  of modern times.There is a a Knock At Midnight and it is now answering the  world.</span>
                  
              
